  "body": "### Description\n\nIn some cases the discovered OIDC metadata does not return some expected URLs, for example, @FroMage has diiscovered that with Facebook all but the required `token_endpoint` URL is returned - so Steph had to disable the discovery and configure all the required endpoint URLs manually.\r\n\r\nIt would be much more user friendlier if the missing piece of metadata can be supplied instead of having to disable the discovery completely   \n\n### Implementation ideas\n\nFallback to the locally provided URL path (relative or absolute) if it is not available in the discovery doc.\r\n\r\nNote I'd like to avoid at this stage to override the values provided in the discovery doc with the local values to avoid some side effects...",
